query:
SELECT
      toDate(month) AS date,
      segment,
      users,
      payment_volume_usd,
      payment_count,
      avg_volume_per_user,
      avg_tx_per_user,
      deposit_volume_usd,
      withdrawal_volume_usd,
      net_flow_usd,
      pct_of_total_volume,
      pct_of_total_users
    FROM dbt.api_execution_gpay_cashback_impact_monthly
    ORDER BY date ASC, segment ASC
